<center><table border=0><tr><td><center><H2><font face=arial>I like Grog, but he's wrong about level restrictions</font></H2></center>
<font face=arial size=2><b>Posted By:</b> <A HREF="/cgi-local/whois2.cgi?TheBlack[BCK]">TheBlack[BCK]</a><br>
